{"data":[{"name":"80:1","price":"Dia (Muhammad) berwajah masam dan berpaling,","arabic":"عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5759,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:2","price":"karena seorang buta telah datang kepadanya (Abdullah bin Ummi Maktum).","arabic":"أَن جَآءَهُ ٱلۡأَعۡمَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5760,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:3","price":"Dan tahukah engkau (Muhammad) barangkali dia ingin menyucikan dirinya (dari dosa),","arabic":"وَمَا يُدۡرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُۥ يَزَّكَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5761,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:4","price":"atau dia (ingin) mendapatkan pengajaran, yang memberi manfaat kepadanya?","arabic":"أَوۡ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5762,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:5","price":"Adapun orang yang merasa dirinya serba cukup (pembesar-pembesar Quraisy),","arabic":"أَمَّا مَنِ ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5763,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:6","price":"maka engkau (Muhammad) memberi perhatian kepadanya,","arabic":"فَأَنتَ لَهُۥ تَصَدَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5764,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:7","price":"padahal tidak ada (cela) atasmu kalau dia tidak menyucikan diri (beriman).","arabic":"وَمَا عَلَيۡكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5765,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:8","price":"Dan adapun orang yang datang kepadamu dengan bersegera (untuk mendapatkan pengajaran),","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسۡعَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5766,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:9","price":"sedang dia takut (kepada Allah),","arabic":"وَهُوَ يَخۡشَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5767,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:10","price":"engkau (Muhammad) malah mengabaikannya.","arabic":"فَأَنتَ عَنۡهُ تَلَهَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5768,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:11","price":"Sekali-kali jangan (begitu)! Sungguh, (ajaran-ajaran Allah) itu suatu peringatan,","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذۡكِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5769,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:12","price":"maka barangsiapa menghendaki, tentulah dia akan memperhatikannya,","arabic":"فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5770,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:13","price":"di dalam kitab-kitab yang dimuliakan (di sisi Allah),","arabic":"فِي صُحُفٖ مُّكَرَّمَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5771,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:14","price":"yang ditinggikan (dan) disucikan,","arabic":"مَّرۡفُوعَةٖ مُّطَهَّرَةِۭ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5772,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:15","price":"di tangan para utusan (malaikat),","arabic":"بِأَيۡدِي سَفَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5773,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:16","price":"yang mulia lagi berbakti.","arabic":"كِرَامِۭ بَرَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5774,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:17","price":"Celakalah manusia! Alangkah kufurnya dia!","arabic":"قُتِلَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَآ أَكۡفَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5775,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:18","price":"Dari apakah Dia (Allah) menciptakannya?","arabic":"مِنۡ أَيِّ شَيۡءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5776,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:19","price":"Dari setetes mani, Dia menciptakannya lalu menentukannya.897)","arabic":"مِن نُّطۡفَةٍ خَلَقَهُۥ فَقَدَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5777,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"*897) Menentukan fase-fase kejadiannya, umurnya, rezekinya dan nasibnya.","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:20","price":"Kemudian jalannya Dia mudahkan,898)","arabic":"ثُمَّ ٱلسَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5778,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"*898) Memudahkan kelahirannya atau memberi persediaan kepadanya untuk menjalani jalan yang benar atau jalan yang sesat.","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:21","price":"kemudian Dia mematikannya lalu menguburkannya,","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَمَاتَهُۥ فَأَقۡبَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5779,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:22","price":"kemudian jika Dia menghendaki, Dia membangkitkannya kembali.","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِذَا شَآءَ أَنشَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5780,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:23","price":"Sekali-kali jangan (begitu)! Dia (manusia) itu belum melaksanakan apa yang Dia (Allah) perintahkan kepadanya.","arabic":"كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقۡضِ مَآ أَمَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5781,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:24","price":"Maka hendaklah manusia itu memperhatikan makanannya,","arabic":"فَلۡيَنظُرِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِۦٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5782,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:25","price":"Kamilah yang telah mencurahkan air melimpah (dari langit),","arabic":"أَنَّا صَبَبۡنَا ٱلۡمَآءَ صَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5783,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:26","price":"kemudian Kami belah bumi dengan sebaik-baiknya,","arabic":"ثُمَّ شَقَقۡنَا ٱلۡأَرۡضَ شَقّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5784,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:27","price":"lalu di sana Kami tumbuhkan biji-bijian,","arabic":"فَأَنۢبَتۡنَا فِيهَا حَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5785,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:28","price":"dan anggur dan sayur-sayuran,","arabic":"وَعِنَبٗا وَقَضۡبٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5786,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:29","price":"dan zaitun dan pohon kurma,","arabic":"وَزَيۡتُونٗا وَنَخۡلٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5787,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:30","price":"dan kebun-kebun (yang) rindang,","arabic":"وَحَدَآئِقَ غُلۡبٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5788,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:31","price":"dan buah-buahan serta rerumputan.","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٗ وَأَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5789,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:32","price":"(Semua itu) untuk kesenanganmu dan untuk hewan-hewan ternakmu.","arabic":"مَّتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5790,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:33","price":"Maka apabila datang suara yang memekakkan (tiupan sangkakala yang kedua),","arabic":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلصَّآخَّةُ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5791,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:34","price":"pada hari itu manusia lari dari saudaranya,","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَفِرُّ ٱلۡمَرۡءُ مِنۡ أَخِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5792,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:35","price":"dan dari ibu dan bapaknya,","arabic":"وَأُمِّهِۦ وَأَبِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5793,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:36","price":"dan dari istri dan anak-anaknya.","arabic":"وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَبَنِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5794,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:37","price":"Setiap orang dari mereka pada hari itu mempunyai urusan yang menyibukkannya.","arabic":"لِكُلِّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ شَأۡنٞ يُغۡنِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5795,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:38","price":"Pada hari itu ada wajah-wajah yang berseri-seri,","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ مُّسۡفِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5796,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:39","price":"tertawa dan gembira ria,","arabic":"ضَاحِكَةٞ مُّسۡتَبۡشِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5797,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:40","price":"dan pada hari itu ada (pula) wajah-wajah yang tertutup debu (suram),","arabic":"وَوُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَلَيۡهَا غَبَرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5798,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:41","price":"tertutup oleh kegelapan (ditimpa kehinaan dan kesusahan).","arabic":"تَرۡهَقُهَا قَتَرَةٌ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5799,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"80:42","price":"Mereka itulah orang-orang kafir yang durhaka.","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡكَفَرَةُ ٱلۡفَجَرَةُ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5800,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"}],"chapter":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa","Chapter Abasa","Surah 80","Chapter 80","He Frowned","عبس"]}